\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/codeMedium(_:)","title":"codeMedium(_:)","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip\/codemedium(_:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"codeMedium"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"OUDSTheme","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract9OUDSThemeC"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI4ViewP"}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSuggestionChip":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"OUDSSuggestionChip","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Suggestion chip is a UI element that allows to present recommended or predictive options based on user’s input or context,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and is commonly used to capture filtering decisions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudssuggestionchip","role":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudscompon